        "description": "Normalized residuals must reach 10⁻⁵ or below. Mass imbalance below 0.05%. Cycle-to-cycle NIH variation below 1% for unsteady simulations. Double precision required. Achieved: residuals 10⁻⁶; imbalance 0.01%; cycle variation 0.3%."
