        "description": "At least two turbulence model variants and two hemolysis model variants must be assessed. Model form uncertainty must be quantified and included in total uncertainty budget. Selected model form must be documented and justified. Achieved: 3 turbulence models × 2 hemolysis models evaluated; model form uncertainty ±9%; SST k-ω + Giersiepen selected and documented in MDD-COU2-v3."
      }
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
