        "description": "All primary model inputs must have documented uncertainty distributions from measurement or literature. Uncertainty propagation to output must be performed. Achieved: viscosity CV 2.1% from viscometry; geometry ±5 µm from CMM; power-law constants from 8-study meta-analysis; all propagated via Sobol (2048 samples)."
